column5: WOO HOO!!  Right on gman!  That's on FAT fish...congrats!
Great fish to be proud of G. WTG.
Awesome. Congrats on the PB little dude.
What a great way to start the year, G! Very nice work... And the only fish of the day- sweet!
No need for the 4rth muskateer to walk the plank any more  . Youve truly earned it now G  Keep up the good work little buddy

My  dad , frankie65 and I went out today. morning  saw no action. Then afternoon came lunch time for us almost always means -- FISH ON, and it did again today.  We netted it and got it in the boat, and it spat the hook before we had a chance to reach in - close call and good net job.  New PB Brownie for me - and jumpy too:    We cruised up and down 3 our 4 times more but no more takers, then headed in thanks dad and Frank you are amazing.
Ya buddy, that's a nice one!!!! Big congrats G-Man!
:thumbsup_anim:  Awesome G-Man.  Great fish.....lol...and great gloves!
Nice job G !!!!!!!!!
Great stuff Lad !! Hopefully we can get you your PB Laker, at the end of July, as well !!
Looks slippery in the first photo! Haha well done G-man!

It was fun watching you catch that beauty G!  What a great relaxing first trip out this year. I said it last year, and will say it again, you have amazing patience for a young man out on the water.  Your dad and mom can be very proud.
That is awesome G-man, now go get another one after the tournament starts
Congrats G. Thats a tank!  Those PB's are gonna start to get harder to find fast the rate you're going
G that is a beauty. Way to go. Congrats on the PB to.
Nice, I haven't gotten a brown yet this year so your ahead of me!
Beauty.  Way to go.
Those jumpy browns are the best kind!  Nice football!
Way to go! Looks like you had lots of fun. That's what it's all about.
Awesome Brown Trout G-man!
Nice fish.  Most of us have had a fish do that to us, less with the camera ready to go.
Well done young man!
That's fantastic.  I love that first picture.  Classic!
Thats an awesome start to the season G, congrats
Atta boy! Nice brown!  S.
Totally awesome fish! Congrats!
Wow!
Probably the nicest fish I've seen this year, G-Man. I wish I could catch one of those. Congrats to you!
Great work, G-Man...that's a fish to be proud of!
Nice-one G-Man!
